name: Hicetnunc Playground
description:
Interactive Hicetnunc logo with multiple backgrounds and options. Controls :
- Change the logo color with 'q'
- Cycle thru through the backgrounds with 1-5
- Pressing 1-5 a second time will change the background color on some patterns
- To save the current image press 's'
- To remove the logo blocks press 6
- Click and drag the image to spin it
- Double click the image to reset the camera
- There may or may not be an easter egg option
